== Events == * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Kumamoto Western School|ja|熊本洋学校|lt=Kumamoto Western School|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
