* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1573|ja|1573rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|September 26|ja|9月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Asai Nagamasa|ja|浅井長政|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|daimyo|ja|大名|qq=draft|qq=draft}} （* {{ill|1545|ja|1545th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1573rd year 9月26日） - {{ill|Asai Masamoto|ja|浅井政元|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|military commander|ja|武将|lt=military commander|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、Nagamasa's younger brother（長政の弟）（* {{ill|1548|ja|1548th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）

