{{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 1''' is the 1st day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） - {{ill|Kumamoto Western School|ja|熊本洋学校|lt=Kumamoto Western School|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}
== Births == * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 17th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） - {{ill|Katō Akedai|ja|加藤暁台|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 、{{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|lt=haiku poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} （+ {{ill|1792|ja|1792nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1865|ja|1865th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 20|ja|10月20日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） - {{ill|Ishibashi Shingetsu|ja|石橋忍月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 、literary critic and novelist（文芸Critic･Novelist）（+ {{ill|1926|ja|1926年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|September 28|ja|9月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） - {{ill|Nagano Uheiji|ja|長野宇平治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 、{{ill|architect|ja|建築家|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} （+ {{ill|1937|ja|1937th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ）
