{{Lunisolar September|qq=}} 
'''September 1''' is the 1st day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） - {{ill|Kumamoto Western School|ja|熊本洋学校|lt=Kumamoto Western School|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 

